We have business together.

48:17.731 --> 48:21.527
Lin, yes. Well, he hasn't been around
for some time.

48:21.527 --> 48:25.405
Last I heard, he had
a rather beautiful Swedish woman

48:25.405 --> 48:27.658
in a suite at the Taj hotel.

48:27.658 --> 48:31.245
And they had plans
to visit Varanasi, I believe.

48:31.245 --> 48:33.455
But you may have missed him already.

48:33.455 --> 48:35.499
But I'll be happy to assist you
in your business--

48:35.499 --> 48:36.583
You can't.

48:46.969 --> 48:49.096
Lisa. It's me, Sebastian.

48:52.224 --> 48:54.810
Sebastian, what are you doing here?
It's dangerous.

48:54.810 --> 48:56.270
I made sure I wasn't followed.

49:01.733 --> 49:03.026
I thought you were gone.

49:06.530 --> 49:07.823
You should have gone.

49:07.823 --> 49:09.283
I won't go without you.

49:11.368 --> 49:13.161
<i>Te amo</i>, Lisa.

49:16.540 --> 49:17.666
I'm sorry.

49:18.834 --> 49:22.754
I'm so sorry for what I said earlier.
I wanna come with you.

49:22.754 --> 49:25.382
Karla's offered to help.
She can get us new travel papers.

49:27.426 --> 49:28.802
It's going to work.

49:33.515 --> 49:34.516
Hey.

49:36.560 --> 49:40.314
Go to Sagar Wada and find
the <i>gora</i> doctor, Linbaba. Okay?

49:40.314 --> 49:43.609
Tell him Didier says to stay there
and not leave the slum.

49:43.609 --> 49:47.696
If he isn't there, you must find Prabhu
and tell Prabhu to come here to see me.

49:47.696 --> 49:50.032
Okay? Just go. Go, go, go. Go, go.
-Okay.

49:55.495 --> 49:57.789
Hey, if you don't let me go,
I'm gonna piss myself.

50:23.148 --> 50:26.401
Any tricks, and I break your legs.

50:37.788 --> 50:39.957
I'm right out there. Hurry up.

51:17.119 --> 51:19.329
Are you still writing a story on Lin?

51:21.707 --> 51:22.708
He knows?

51:25.586 --> 51:27.004
Did he send you here?

51:27.004 --> 51:28.881
I came here to ask you to stop.

51:35.637 --> 51:38.891
Lindsay Ford is the name of a dead man.

51:38.891 --> 51:40.225
Did you know that already?

51:40.225 --> 51:41.977
Who Lin was doesn't matter.

51:41.977 --> 51:45.689
What matters is who he is now,
the work he's doing in Sagar Wada.

51:46.565 --> 51:48.984
If you publish your story,
he'll have to leave Bombay.

51:48.984 --> 51:50.736
He doesn't deserve that.

51:53.238 --> 51:56.408
Plenty of us deserve to be punished
for the shit we've done,

51:56.408 --> 51:57.826
but Lin isn't one of them.

52:01.496 --> 52:03.332
What is it that you do, Karla?

52:03.332 --> 52:06.793
I mean, we hang out in Reynaldo's
and we all have fun.

52:07.336 --> 52:12.132
We are friendly,
but we're not really friends, as such.

52:16.553 --> 52:20.724
Look, I like Lin, okay?
But this is what I do.

52:21.308 --> 52:24.770
I'm a journalist. And Lin's a story.

52:27.523 --> 52:29.358
I make deals happen that shouldn't.

52:33.237 --> 52:36.573
If you drop that story on Lin,
I'll give you a better one.

52:38.492 --> 52:39.493
What is it?

52:40.619 --> 52:44.790
Corruption, bribery, sex, and murders.

52:49.294 --> 52:53.715
I can give you a story on how
a Bombay gangster is using them all

52:53.715 --> 52:56.260
to try and get his hands on
the Sagar Wada slums.

52:57.845 --> 52:59.012
All right.

52:59.805 --> 53:00.806
I'm listening.

53:02.140 --> 53:05.185
First, I need your word
that you'll walk away from Lin.

53:05.894 --> 53:09.439
Whatever happens,
he gets to stay in Bombay.

53:16.989 --> 53:17.990
Come inside.

53:36.550 --> 53:38.218
No, I'm all right. I'm all right.

53:48.395 --> 53:49.938
I'm sorry I shot him, Sarge.

53:50.772 --> 53:53.650
So am I, Son. So am I.

53:55.903 --> 53:58.280
Still, we made
a good collar tonight, right?

53:58.280 --> 54:00.657
Well, it's a result, either way.

54:01.700 --> 54:04.286
Tonight was a fucking shambles.

54:05.829 --> 54:09.458
Cops killing fellas like that
turn them into heroes for other scumbags.

54:11.543 --> 54:15.923
And now Pendergast can't
tell us where the little bastard is.

54:16.924 --> 54:17.925
And I don't know--

54:17.925 --> 54:20.719
That's a fucking result,
somehow in your small mind.

54:43.075 --> 54:45.994
This a fucking wind-up?

55:04.805 --> 55:07.641
Don't tell me you're leaving.
I need someone to get drunk with.

55:07.641 --> 55:09.810
Lin, we're both leaving.

55:09.810 --> 55:11.979
Mate, I just got here.
I'm gonna get shit-faced.

55:11.979 --> 55:14.481
Lin, <i>on y va</i>.
We can have a drink at my place.

55:24.575 --> 55:26.910
Did something happen?
-I'll explain later.

55:33.667 --> 55:36.170
What's going on?
-I'm in a little trouble.

55:36.170 --> 55:38.380
I need your help but elsewhere.

55:38.380 --> 55:40.048
Now, let's go.
-More trouble?

55:40.048 --> 55:42.801
I left you alone for six hours.
What's going on?

55:44.178 --> 55:45.179
Let's move on.

55:59.276 --> 56:01.445
Is he following you?
-Move on. Move on. Move on.

56:04.156 --> 56:05.157
Come.

56:15.626 --> 56:18.045
What do you want?
Why the fuck are you following him?

56:18.045 --> 56:20.839
Leave me-- Leave me--
-Why the fuck--

56:21.715 --> 56:23.717
Why are you following him?
-Not me. You.

56:23.717 --> 56:26.178
He's following you, Lin!
-Why you fucking following him?

56:26.178 --> 56:27.804
And there'll be others!

56:40.526 --> 56:41.735
What's going on?

56:42.694 --> 56:44.112
What have you done, Linbaba?

56:45.697 --> 56:46.698
What have I done?

56:49.117 --> 56:50.494
Jesus Christ.
